Case No. 15,599. UNITED STATES v. LILIENTHAL. Circuit Court, S. D. New York. 1873. UNITED STATES (LILIENTHAL’S TOBACCO v.). See Case No. 16,106a.

[Affirming Case No. 16,105. Affirmed by supreme court. Lilienthal v. U. S., 97 U. S. 237. Cited in Hawloetz v. Kass, 25 Fed. 765. Nowhere reported; opinion not now accessible.]
